<br>
Combat Fury -- If a Rogue wants to make good use of this, I seriously suggest getting that dex up.  It makes Critical hits proc a -lot- more often.  This isn't just an opinion.  You can tell a -huge- difference.  Moreso than strength.  <br>
<br>
Makes a big difference with proc'n weapons, too. <br>
<br>
Helps with throwing weapons.<br>
<br>
